Description: Provides access to tidy and curated data from Argentina's 
    official population censuses, covering national totals and data for the 
    24 jurisdictions for 1970 and 1980. The package is designed to 
    facilitate the exploration and reuse of historical census information 
    through tools for data retrieval, validation, and interactive visualization.
